tirehockeyschool.ca/video/mandatory-equipment \"Mandatory Equipment\"]\n* [http://www.sihrhockey.org/origins_main.cfm SIHR \u2013 The Origins of Hockey]\n* [http://hockey-history.com History of ice hockey]\n* [http://www.hockeymap.com/ Map of College & Pro Ice Hockey Teams in Canada and USA]\n\n{{IIHF}}\n{{Team Sport}}\n{{Ice Hockey Leagues}}\n{{Winter Olympic sports}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Ice Hockey}}\n[[Category:Ice hockey]]\n[[Category:Former Summer Olympic sports]]\n[[Category:Hockey]]\n[[Category:Ice sports|hockey]]\n[[Category:Ice skating]]\n[[Category:National symbols of Canada]]\n[[Category:Sports originating in Canada]]\n[[Category:Team sports]]\n[[Category:Variations of hockey]]\n[[Category:Winter sports]]\n[[Category:Winter Olympic sports]]\n[[Category:Canadian culture]]\n", "name_user": "72.88.215.205", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "(\u2192\u200eHistory)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ice_hockey"}
